abstract: Investors have returned to the mortgage-backed market, as commercial property prices are perceived to have hit bottom.
snippet: Investors have returned to the mortgage-backed market, as commercial property prices are perceived to have hit bottom.
lead_paragraph: Once dominant, and then dormant, commercial real estate loans are beginning to show signs of life on the trading floor after a two-year slump.

headline.main: Banks Edge Cautiously Back Into Commercial Mortgage-Backed Bonds
headline.print_headline: Banks Edge Cautiously Back Into Commercial Mortgage-Backed Bonds
